QuestData.Title: Home Is Where the Frogs Are
QuestData.Description:
All the frogs are rounded up, $n! I guess we're, uh, taking the frogs to Akora anyway. They'll be safe at the Life Pools until the hornswogs get bored and move on.
Um, well, I guess we didn't find anything to cheer up Akora. I hope she understands...
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Keshki back at the Life Pools to release the rescued frogs.
